=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7dfeb4690cc5eeecfe2e8ddf5ff7b4a3cde37e","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"小小虫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b20a90766d4d3c8ece5fd0574c52e0079d165db","tid":1406154,"uid":156466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a7dfeb4690cc5eeecfe2e8ddf5ff7b4a3cde37e","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"小小虫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"你好巴打 <br />\n依鍋野 唔洗理大家係邊個 一條心<br />\n幫得就幫 <br />\n點樣幫到義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b30b19a0d64bac5378d53e72b3644093109ee5","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b20a90766d4d3c8ece5fd0574c52e0079d165db","tid":1406154,"uid":156466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a7dfeb4690cc5eeecfe2e8ddf5ff7b4a3cde37e","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"小小虫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"你好巴打 <br />\n依鍋野 唔洗理大家係邊個 一條心<br />\n幫得就幫 <br />\n點樣幫到義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"🌐港人自救 - 借宿 &amp; 流動救護車Channel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=f9bede4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q</a><br />\n<br />\n【早晨手足】<br />\n尋晚義載做到admin爆哂廠，因為有心手足實在太多，我地決定改做的士call台方式。<br />\n<br />\n1. 義載<br />\n需要義載手足請將確切地點、目的地、人數、性別send俾admin<br />\n目的地九龍、港島請pm @holdourhand<br />\n新東 @keepgoingfight <br />\n新西 @irapthegovernment<br />\n<br />\nAdmin會出broadcast召車，車手可跟單pm相應admin接。未有單時可街上接。<br />\n___<br />\n2. 救護車服務<br />\n所有分區救護員已merge做一team，有事佢地已經自動落場，但如果手足有需要急救但現場搵唔到急救員都可以pm admin<br />\n@dogsbitehard<br />\n@NoworNever_HK <br />\n<br />\n有興趣成為First aider請pm @NoworNever_HK <br />\n____<br />\n3. 求宿求飯傾計有咩要幫手都好，pm @irapthegovernment @keepgoingfight <br />\n如求宿請註明區域、性別、怕唔性貓狗。<br />\n宿位飯位區域見下表宿飯總滙<br />\n____<br />\n4. 餐廳供飯<br />\n餐廳供膳係其中一位ADMIN好熟嘅CAFE，<br />\n佢地由老闆到員工都支持各位手足，絕對可以放心。<br />\n暫時運作方式係：<br />\n1️⃣需要嘅手足PM @keepgoingfight TelegramID同食飯時間<br />\n（Admin會PM返鋪頭名同地址比你）<br />\n2️⃣Admin每朝會集齊人數比老闆<br />\n3️⃣大家跟時間上去食飯就OK！（食幾多餐都得！）<br />\n<br />\n因為未知需要幾多份餐，暫時唔開放捐款，<br />\n之前聯絡過想課金既朋友留意。<br />\n<br />\n-以下為抒情文-<br />\n其實比起物資同錢，班細路最需要嘅係實際支持，<br />\n所以8月5希望大家一齊罷工，唔係請假罷工，<br />\n係真正癱瘓個城市。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家再諗真D，你罷工一日，可能可以令班細路唔洗坐監同食蛋。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果手足可以提供住家飯（可以供埋宿優先）可以📩pm：<br />\n@keepgoingfight<br />\n@holdourhand<br />\n@kuroihitsujishirokuma<br />\n@dogsbitehard<br />\n註明供飯時間、區域、有無寵物。<br />\n如可供埋宿，請註明埋可供宿至幾時、可接收人數、有否限男女、telegram ID。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️為防有鬼，請自動影一影個人八達通、學生證、卡片或會員證俾我地做記錄<br />\n遮部分名部分樣for safety reason<br />\n____<br />\n宿飯總滙<br />\n<br />\n【鑑於宿位眾多，我地暫時只列地區，有需要隨時PM查詢啦！】<br />\n<br />\n外國<br />\nNew York<br />\n<br />\n新界（*有住家飯）<br />\n西貢| 坑口| 將軍澳*| 寶琳*<br />\n葵芳| 葵興| 葵涌| 荃灣| 荃灣西 <br />\n元朗| 元朗世宙| 元朗錦繡| 錦上路*  <br />\n朗屏*| 朗屏工業區  <br />\n兆康| 屯門| 屯門西鐵站| 屯門碼頭| 屯門藍地<br />\n天水圍*| 八鄉| 八鄉錦田| 深井<br />\n沙田*|石門*| 大圍| 馬鞍山*| 火炭 <br />\n大埔| 大埔林村| 大埔近太和站<br />\n粉嶺| 西沙路*| 上水<br />\n<br />\n港島（*有住家飯）<br />\n杏花邨| 柴灣*| 筲箕灣*<br />\n西灣河*| 太古*| 鰂魚涌<br />\n北角| 砲台山| 天后 <br />\n銅鑼灣| 灣仔* <br />\n中環半山| 上環 <br />\n西營盤| 石塘咀 <br />\n堅離地城| 港大站<br />\n南區| 香港仔| 黃竹坑<br />\n<br />\n九龍（*有住家飯）<br />\n觀塘| 油塘* <br />\n秀茂坪| 牛頭角*| 九龍灣| 安達<br />\n九龍城*| 土瓜灣<br />\n新蒲崗| 慈雲山 <br />\n旺角*| 太子| 大角咀<br />\n何文田| 紅磡 *<br />\n佐敦*| 尖沙咀<br />\n深水埗| 長沙灣| 荔枝角<br />\n<br />\n離島（*有住家飯）<br />\n東涌| 青衣北| 青衣<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n粉嶺區教會及大圍站教會<br />\n3/8起可以提供小食及住宿，需預約，有需要請pm admin<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n灣仔cafe 可以提供食物、wifi、充電、廁所<br />\n星期一至五 1400-2100<br />\n星期六日 1100-2100<br />\n發夢後過夜10位（無床）<br />\n<br />\n有需要pm admin"},{"pid":"7a006d6af03068abe96169d16d29f92b4739eca9","tid":1406154,"uid":84934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"支持巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前幫襯過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dfb0440641d5014dd598ffd93e59396876ef65","tid":1406154,"uid":156466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70b30b19a0d64bac5378d53e72b3644093109ee5","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b20a90766d4d3c8ece5fd0574c52e0079d165db","tid":1406154,"uid":156466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a7dfeb4690cc5eeecfe2e8ddf5ff7b4a3cde37e","tid":1406154,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"小小虫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"你好巴打 <br />\n依鍋野 唔洗理大家係邊個 一條心<br />\n幫得就幫 <br />\n點樣幫到義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"rep